high_descs: remove mug from inside coffee maker
wash and remove full mug from sink
anns.task_desc: put washed mug full of water inside coffee maker

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug in the coffee maker.
Wash the mug in the sink.
Put the mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean cup in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Move to the coffee machine on the counter to your right.
Pick up the dirty mug on the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the sink left of the coffee machine.
Wash the mug in the sink with water, fill the mug with water.
Bring the filled mug to the coffee machine on the right.
Put the filled mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned, mug full of water on the coffee machine.
